{"word":"G2418 - ἱερουργέω - hierourgéō - hee-er-oorg-eh'-o - Minister","slug":"G2418","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱερουργέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hierourgéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hee-er-oorg-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Minister"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x03C1;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - hierourgeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hee-er-oorg-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2411\">G2411</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2041\">G2041</a>; to <i>be a temple worker</i>, that is, <i>officiate as a priest</i> (figuratively): - minister."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420\">G2420</a>, <a href=\"#/G749\">G749</a>"}]}